店家
1. 功能：取得店家資料。Method: GET。URL: /api/shop/:id
SELECT `user_ID`, `shop_copy`, `precautions` FROM `product_shop` WHERE user_ID = ?


2. 功能：新增店家。Method: POST。URL: /api/shop

INSERT INTO `product_shop`(`user_ID`, `shop_copy`, `precautions`) 
VALUES ('[value-1]','[value-2]','[value-3]')

3. 功能：修改店家。Method: PUT。URL: /api/shop/:id

UPDATE `product_shop` SET `user_ID`='[value-1]',
`shop_copy`='[value-2]',`precautions`='[value-3]' WHERE user_ID = ?